title: Double Trouble 2022: Colts & Jaguars
description:
Field Yates and Daniel Dopp tackle a Double Trouble on the Colts and Jaguars, including if Jonathan Taylor is a no brainer as the 1st overall pick. Then, the guys talk how you should approach your drafts in Non-PPR leagues this year.
